sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Пользователь
    participant Telegram as Telegram Bot API
    participant Service as internal/bot.Service
    participant Quotes as internal/quotes.Client
    participant TgSend as Telegram Bot API

    User->>Telegram: /quote
    Telegram->>Service: Update с командой /quote
    Service->>Quotes: GetQuote(ctx)
    Quotes->>Quotes: HTTP запрос к Forismatic
    Quotes-->>Service: Quote (текст, автор)
    Service->>TgSend: Send(Message)
    TgSend-->>User: Сообщение с цитатой